{"tid":2029844,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【曲撚夠未】國安法只係單方面屠殺，外國做野先會攬炒","createTime":"2020-05-22T12:27:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T15:24:39.000Z","uid":15696,"like":252,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":88,"replies":[{"pid":"008d7e07e96d1eb168fbfe235a0dc695deedf612","tid":2029844,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:27:24.000Z","msg":"Copy人不滅巴打<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">借個位：黑色五毛風向警告，大量五毛正在吹襲連登</span></strong><br />\n正視聽，<span style=\"color: red;\">國安法唔係攬炒，美國做野先係</span><br />\n<br />\n大家<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比五毛帶風向去支持國安法，否則會比對家spin成香港人支持國安法</span>。只有<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人強烈反對下強行通過，美國才有做野的理由</span>。大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，<span style=\"color: red;\">英國點日落都好，香港問題上都係重要持分者</span>，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就三萬幾人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span>"},{"pid":"a9a297d66ab6f74f47e35b06ee24ec59f3c383e8","tid":2029844,"uid":15696,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:29:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仲係度扮藍 話歡迎國安法<br />\n我屌哂你哋老母 有時間去社交平台打網戰啦</span>"},{"pid":"bc0a774992a2b799c54ddafcdd7b2a847c7f4969","tid":2029844,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:29:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac